  <h2>The Discipline is:</h2>
  <p>suspension from the bus and  transportation is not listed on my child’s IEP.</p>
</div>
  <h2>Response:</h2>
  <p>Because transportation is not on  your child&rsquo;s IEP a suspension from the bus  is not a <span class="def" id="change-of-placement">change of placement*</span> and does not count as a removal of a child from  school. Therefore, you must provide transportation to and from school  for your child.  </p>
  <p class="tip">Tip: If the behavior on the bus is similar to the behavior in  school that is already addressed by an IEP, you should request an IEP meeting  to discuss addressing the bus behavior in your child’s IEP and <span class="def" id="bip">Behavioral  Intervention Plan (BIP)*</span>.</p>
